1971;;Red Sky at Morning;;American;;James Goldstone;;Desi Arnaz, Jr., Catherine Burns, Richard Crenna;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Red_Sky_at_Morning_(1971_film);;The film follows Josh Arnold (Thomas), whose family relocates to Corazon Sagrado, New Mexico during World War II. The title of the book/film comes from a line in an ancient mariner's rhyme, "Red sky at morning, sailor take warning"